# HiveKeeper — Cloudflare Pages URL rewrites
# Cleans up the URLs shown to web users while keeping original file paths
# intact for the iOS and Android Median wrappers.
#
# Status codes:
#   200 = REWRITE  (URL stays masked, content served silently from target)
#   301 = REDIRECT (browser URL changes to the target path)

# Root of site serves the app — gethivekeeper.com is now THE app
/            /hivekeeper-beta1.html   200

# Optional clean aliases in case you want to link to /app or /dev specifically
/app         /hivekeeper-beta1.html   200
/app/*       /hivekeeper-beta1.html   200

# Development build for beta testers
/dev         /hivekeeper-dev.html     200
/dev/*       /hivekeeper-dev.html     200
